-- Aker Solutions, FMC, Vetco Among Bidders for Husky's Liwan, Upstream Says
-- Marianne Stigset
-- 2010-08-06T07:08:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/aker-solutions-fmc-vetco-among-bidders-for-husky-s-liwan-upstream-says.html

          
          
             Aker Solutions ASA, FMC Technologies
Inc., Cameron International Corp. and Vetco Gray Inc. submitted
bids for a turnkey contract at Husky Energy Inc.’s Liwan 3-1 gas
project in China,  Upstream reported , without citing where it got
the information.  
 The companies are in the process of clarifying their offers
and Husky may shortlist as many as three before selecting a
winner, Upstream said. Liwan 3-1 in the South China Sea is
China’s first deepwater development, Upstream said.  
